metadata.name: TOXICOIN .1
metadata.description:
TOXICOIN is a utility token made by holytoxic // 2022-2023

PHASE 1// Top 5 holders of TOXICOIN will be awarded with an edition of the first 3 pieces in ‘editions of toxicity’ which is published by holytoxic via manifold. Claims of TOXICOIN will be through a claim page and claim window will be open until 26 December 2022, Monday,  
17:00 PM GMT +3. Each TOXICOIN will be listed at 0.0069 ETH at all times. Daily leaderboards will be shared on Twitter and ‘Eden’ Discord channel. 

PHASE 2// Second supply of TOXICOIN and burn mechanics with more awards within ‘editions of toxicity.
